{"tid":458152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因為我禮拜六日唔沖涼 老母要同我斷絕母子關係","createTime":"2017-11-04T14:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T15:18:22.000Z","uid":148315,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7933299fb742d2e86afdff589bf66f7e485cbb5f","tid":458152,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"老母竟然同我講點解可以唔日日沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢講 勁多研究同報告證實咗冇必要日日沖涼，日日沖甚至會影響健康 佢話一句我唔想睇就ko我<br />\n大佬啊我十幾廿歲人沖唔沖涼使你管啊，我星期六日唔使返工返學先唔沖，又唔會好污糟好臭<br />\n跟住又話養到你咁大點解可以咁叛逆咁不孝，令到佢好傷心，唔沖涼唔好認佢做老母，我聽到眼都突埋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本唔使日日沖涼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點可以唔日日沖"},{"pid":"8343e84e6419390b35dbd473ab8fb71bd3cd40a9","tid":458152,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"我成個月唔沖都試過啦 怕乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f68f98b70d81148394bfbc99d3290ebe11e862d","tid":458152,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"好撚污糟"},{"pid":"fad2a29d0a553468e276185bd91c2b59b917836b","tid":458152,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"冬天果陣會入去禁十分鐘電話扮沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}